# This is a `<h1>` tag
## This is an `<h2>` tag  
###### This is an `<h6>` tag  

## LISTS:  
### Unordered-  
* Item 1  
* Item 2  
* Item 2a   
    * Item 2b  
### Ordered-  
1. Item 1  
2. Item 2   
3. Item 3    
    * Item 3a     
    * Item 3b    
    
## EMPHASIS:
*This text will be italic*  
_This will also be italic_  
**This text will be bold**   
__This will also be bold__  
*You **can** combine them*
